snippet: Rafael Nadal defeated his fellow Spaniard Daniel Gimeno-Traver, 6-1, 6-4, to reach the semifinals of the VTR Open in Vina del Mar, Chile.
abstract: Rafael Nadal defeats Daniel Gimeno-Traver to reach VTR Open tennis tournament semifinals in Vina del Mar, Chile.
